  <title>SCARA</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>SCARA-Robot</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="width:459px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2">SCARA</text> is an acronym that stands for <text style="text-decoration:underline;">Selective Compliance Assembly Robot Arm</text> or <text style="text-decoration:underline;">Selective Compliance Articulated Robot Arm</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">It is a Robot that looks similar to the human arm. A servomotor between the Base and Upper-Arm at the Shoulder, a servomotor between the Upper-Arm and Fore-Arm at the Elbow, and a servomotor between the Fore-Arm and the Hand at the Wrist. There is a tool in the hand at the distal end.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
</topic>
